{
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "file_path": "bg_underground_city",
      "wait_tween_end": "1",
      "delay": "0.8"
    },
    {
      "type": "sound",
      "sound_type": "bgm",
      "file_path": "bgm_wonder"
    },
    {
      "type": "talk",
      "is_center": "1",
      "talk_content": "（石阶尽头——一座地下的城市在眼前展开。）"
    },
    {
      "type": "talk",
      "is_center": "1",
      "talk_content": "（金色的光从穹顶倾泻而下。街道由古老的石板铺成，两侧的建筑发出柔和的荧光。人们穿着我们从未见过的衣服，平静地走过。）"
    },
    {
      "type": "tachie",
      "tachies": {
        "saya": {
          "file_path": "saya_determined",
          "type": "show"
        },
        "kenta": {
          "file_path": "kenta_amazed",
          "type": "show"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "talk",
      "talker": "健太",
      "talk_content": "这不可能是真的……我们在地底下！这么大的空间怎么支撑得住的？",
      "avatar_path": "kenta"
    },
    {
      "type": "talk",
      "talker": "小夜",
      "talk_content": "这里是'镜城'。和地上的世界一一对应——但又完全不同。",
      "avatar_path": "saya"
    },
    {
      "type": "talk",
      "talker": "小夜",
      "talk_content": "我从小就能找到通往这里的路。但其他人不行——除非在满月之夜。",
      "avatar_path": "saya"
    },
    {
      "type": "tachie",
      "tachies": {
        "elder": {
          "file_path": "elder_wise",
          "type": "show"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "talk",
      "talker": "长老",
      "talk_content": "小夜，你又带了客人来啊。……而且是满月之夜。",
      "avatar_path": "elder"
    },
    {
      "type": "talk",
      "talker": "长老",
      "talk_content": "孩子——你们正站在两个世界的夹缝里。留下来？还是回去？",
      "avatar_path": "elder"
    },
    {
      "type": "talk",
      "talker": "长老",
      "talk_content": "镜城的居民曾几何时也住在你们的世界。但有些真理太危险，所以我们将它藏在了地下。",
      "avatar_path": "elder"
    },
    {
      "type": "tachie",
      "tachies": {
        "saya": {
          "file_path": "saya_surprised",
          "type": "change"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "talk",
      "talker": "小夜",
      "talk_content": "什么真理？你从来没有告诉过我——",
      "avatar_path": "saya"
    },
    {
      "type": "talk",
      "talker": "长老",
      "talk_content": "因为你还没有准备好。但现在——你带来了两个人。这就够了。",
      "avatar_path": "elder"
    },
    {
      "type": "talk",
      "talker": "长老",
      "talk_content": "镜城的核心是'记录之书'。它记载了地上世界所有已经发生和将要发生的事。",
      "avatar_path": "elder"
    },
    {
      "type": "talk",
      "talker": "长老",
      "talk_content": "触碰书的人——能选择自己的未来。但也必须承担相应的代价。",
      "avatar_path": "elder"
    },
    {
      "type": "tachie",
      "tachies": {
        "elder": {
          "file_path": "elder_wise",
          "type": "close"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "talk",
      "is_center": "1",
      "talk_content": "（长老退后一步。他身后的墙壁缓缓升起——露出一本悬浮在半空中的巨大书卷。）"
    },
    {
      "type": "sound",
      "sound_type": "oneSound",
      "file_path": "sfx_book_reveal"
    },
    {
      "type": "talk",
      "is_center": "1",
      "talk_content": "（书页翻动着，每一页上都以流动的光写满了文字。有些是过去，有些是未来。有些页是空白的——等待着被写下。）"
    },
    {
      "type": "talk",
      "talker": "小夜",
      "talk_content": "这就是……我一直想找的东西。未来的答案。",
      "avatar_path": "saya"
    },
    {
      "type": "tachie",
      "tachies": {
        "kenta": {
          "file_path": "kenta_serious",
          "type": "change"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "talk",
      "talker": "健太",
      "talk_content": "等一下。如果这本书能写未来——那我们的人生算什么？",
      "avatar_path": "kenta"
    },
    {
      "type": "talk",
      "talker": "健太",
      "talk_content": "是被安排好的剧本？还是我们可以自己选择？",
      "avatar_path": "kenta"
    },
    {
      "type": "talk",
      "is_center": "1",
      "talk_content": "（沉默。书页的光芒微微闪烁，仿佛在等待。）"
    },
    {
      "type": "branch",
      "options": {
        "3A": {
          "text": "「我要触碰那本书。」"
        },
        "3B": {
          "text": "「未来应该由自己创造。」"
        },
        "3C": {
          "text": "「小夜，你怎么想？」"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "talk",
      "branch": "3A",
      "talker": "我",
      "talk_content": "我要触碰那本书。即便命运是写好的——我也想看它一眼。"
    },
    {
      "type": "talk",
      "branch": "3B",
      "talker": "我",
      "talk_content": "未来应该由自己创造。这本书——只记录了过去。空白的页面不正是留给我们的吗？"
    },
    {
      "type": "talk",
      "branch": "3C",
      "talker": "我",
      "talk_content": "小夜，你怎么想？这是你一直追寻的地方。"
    },
    {
      "type": "tachie",
      "tachies": {
        "saya": {
          "file_path": "saya_teary",
          "type": "change"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "talk",
      "branch": "3C",
      "talker": "小夜",
      "talk_content": "我……我不知道。我一直以为找到答案就能安心。但现在——",
      "avatar_path": "saya"
    },
    {
      "type": "talk",
      "talker": "小夜",
      "talk_content": "也许健太说得对。真正重要的是我们现在做的选择。",
      "avatar_path": "saya"
    },
    {
      "type": "tachie",
      "tachies": {
        "saya": {
          "file_path": "saya_smile",
          "type": "change"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "talk",
      "talker": "小夜",
      "talk_content": "来吧——不管书里写了什么，我们一起面对。",
      "avatar_path": "saya"
    },
    {
      "type": "talk",
      "is_center": "1",
      "talk_content": "（三人同时伸出手。指尖触碰书页的瞬间——整个世界变成了白色。）"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "file_path": "bg_white_space",
      "wait_tween_end": "1",
      "delay": "0.5"
    },
    {
      "type": "tachie",
      "tachies": {
        "saya": {
          "file_path": "saya_smile",
          "type": "close"
        },
        "kenta": {
          "file_path": "kenta_amazed",
          "type": "close"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "sound",
      "sound_type": "oneSound",
      "file_path": "sfx_final_chime"
    },
    {
      "type": "talk",
      "is_center": "1",
      "talk_content": "（书页上浮现出新的文字——空白的页面正在被填充。）"
    },
    {
      "type": "talk",
      "is_center": "1",
      "talk_content": "（不是预测。不是命运。而是他们刚才做出的选择——被铭刻为新的历史。）"
    },
    {
      "type": "talk",
      "is_center": "1",
      "talk_content": "（未来，原来一直被握在自己手中。）"
    },
    {
      "type": "event",
      "event_name": "finale"
    },
    {
      "type": "talk",
      "is_center": "1",
      "talk_content": "—— 镜城物语 · 完 ——"
    },
    {
      "type": "goto",
      "file_path": "End"
    }
  ]
}
